Feature: User Valid Login
  As a registered user
  I want to be able to sign in to the application
  So that I can access to the user dashboard

  Background:
    Given the login page is displayed

  Scenario: Successful login with valid credentials
    When I enter the valid username 'user'
    And I enter the valid password 'pass'
    And I click the 'Sign In' button
    Then I should be able to observe the user dashboard
;
Feature: Add a New User
  As a signed-in user
  I want to be able to add a new user with a specific role
  So that they can access the system to create surveys

  Background:
    Given I am signed in
    And I can see my dashboard

  Scenario: Successfully adding a new user with the Researcher role
    When I navigate to the 'Users' menu
    And I click on the 'Add User' option
    And I type 'testar-researcher' in the name field
    And I click the input element to select the role 'Researcher'
    And I confirm the addition
    Then 'testar-researcher' should appear in the list of existing users
